      <scene id="2200" sNumber="2200" sType="scocontent" continueBtnType="DONE">
        <sceneitems>
          <ui uid="0" type="sceneHeader">
            <header id="h1">
              <![CDATA[Loyalty and Profitability]]>
</header>
          </ui>
        </sceneitems>
        <slides>
          <slide sNumber="2205" type="TextImageReplace" animType="timesync" endType="continue">
            <ui uid="2" type="BodyText" width="680" height="180" x="center" y="270" margin="0" fontAlign="center" effect="none" time="2" ease="QuintEaseOut" trans="slideLeft" syncType="replace">
              <bodyBullet id="bb1" timeIn=".5" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[In fact, Chrysler Group is changing the focus of its business from a customer satisfaction orientation to customer loyalty.
In some markets, SSI and CSI measurements have already been replaced with the Customer Promoter Score.]]>
</bodyBullet>
            </ui>
            <ui uid="1" type="BodyImage" width="375" height="250" x="center" y="top" margin="10" scaleMode="none" time=".5" trans="fadeOn" ease="QuintEaseOut" syncType="replace">
              <bodyImage id="i1" url="2205_1.jpg" timeIn=".2" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[image1]]>
</bodyImage>
            </ui>
          </slide>
          <slide sNumber="2210" type="TextImageReplace" animType="timesync" endType="continue">
            <ui uid="2" type="BodyText" width="680" height="180" x="center" y="270" margin="0" fontAlign="center" effect="none" time="2" trans="slideLeft" ease="QuintEaseOut" syncType="replace">
              <bodyBullet id="bb1" timeIn=".5" timeOut="10">
                <![CDATA[For many years in the U.S., we’ve been measuring customer satisfaction with the sales and service experience.  And for many years, the satisfaction scores have been trending upward!]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb2" timeIn="10.5" timeOut="20">
                <![CDATA[But it clearly isn’t enough.  While the satisfaction scores have been rising, our customers’ loyalty to the company, the brand, and their dealership has NOT been following suit!]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb3" timeIn="20.5" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[Our “satisfied” customers are defecting to other brands, and to other dealerships.]]>
</bodyBullet>
            </ui>
            <ui uid="1" type="BodyImage" width="375" height="250" x="center" y="top" margin="10" scaleMode="none" time="3" trans="fadeOn" ease="QuintEaseOut" syncType="replace">
              <bodyImage id="i1" url="2210_1.jpg" timeIn=".2" timeOut="999" time=".1">
                <![CDATA[image1]]>
</bodyImage>
            </ui>
            <ui uid="5" type="slideEndNote" fontSize="10" trans="fadeIn" ease="QuintEaseOut">
              <bodyNote id="gn1" timeIn="4" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[*Graph based on U.S. data.]]>
</bodyNote>
            </ui>
          </slide>
          <slide sNumber="2215" type="TextImageAround" animType="timesync" endType="Continue">
            <ui uid="2" type="BodyText" width="280" height="200" x="center" y="200" fontAlign="center" effect="none" time="1" trans="slideup" ease="QuintEaseOut" syncType="replace">
              <bodyBullet id="bb1" timeIn=".5" timeOut="10">
                <![CDATA[Fortunately, this lack of correlation between “satisfaction” and loyalty is not limited to our industry alone – and it has been the subject of much research in recent years.]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb2" timeIn="10.5" timeOut="20">
                <![CDATA[Leading researchers on loyalty identified a way to link customer attitudes to their behavior – and also to company growth.]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb3" timeIn="20.5" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[The measurement is based on customers' responses to one simple question – the one that has come to be known as “the ultimate question”… and it is the basis of the Customer Promoter Score.]]>
</bodyBullet>
            </ui>
            <ui uid="1" type="BodyImage" width="240" height="160" x="center" y="top" margin="10" effect="none" scaleMode="none" centerIt="true" time="1" trans="slideup" ease="QuintEaseOut">
              <bodyImage id="img1" url="2215_1.jpg" timeIn=".2" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[main image]]>
</bodyImage>
            </ui>
            <ui uid="1" type="BodyImage" x="left" y="top" margin="20" width="150" height="100" effect="none" scaleMode="none" trans="slideright" ease="QuintEaseOut" time="1" syncType="buildy" yPad="7">
              <bodyImage id="img2" url="2215_2.jpg" timeIn="2" timeOut="999" yPad="0">
                <![CDATA[img2]]>
</bodyImage>
              <bodyImage id="img4" url="2215_4.jpg" timeIn="4" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[img4]]>
</bodyImage>
              <bodyImage id="img6" url="2215_6.jpg" timeIn="6" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[img6]]>
</bodyImage>
              <bodyImage id="img8" url="2215_8.jpg" timeIn="8" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[img8]]>
</bodyImage>
            </ui>
            <ui uid="1" type="BodyImage" x="right" y="top" margin="20" width="150" height="100" effect="none" scaleMode="none" trans="slideleft" ease="QuintEaseOut" time="1" syncType="buildy" yPad="7">
              <bodyImage id="img3" url="2215_3.jpg" timeIn="3" timeOut="999" yPad="0">
                <![CDATA[img3]]>
</bodyImage>
              <bodyImage id="img5" url="2215_5.jpg" timeIn="5" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[img5]]>
</bodyImage>
              <bodyImage id="img7" url="2215_7.jpg" timeIn="7" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[img7]]>
</bodyImage>
              <bodyImage id="img9" url="2215_9.jpg" timeIn="9" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[img9]]>
</bodyImage>
            </ui>
          </slide>
          <slide sNumber="2220" type="BulletImageBuild" animType="animsync" endType="Continue">
            <ui uid="3" type="bodyBullet" width="500" x="left" y="top" margin="10" time="1" trans="slideRight" ease="QuintEaseOut" syncType="buildy" yPad="10">
              <bodyBullet id="bb1" order="2" yPad="0">
                <![CDATA[And that question is, “Would you recommend us to a friend or colleague?”]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb2" order="6">
                <![CDATA[<li>Research found that the more likely a customer was to recommend a company or product, the more likely they were to remain loyal to that company and its products themselves over the long term</li>]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb3" order="10">
                <![CDATA[<li>Research also shows that just because a customer indicated they were “satisfied” with a particular experience, didn’t mean they’d necessarily be willing to recommend the company – or remain loyal to them over time</li>]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb4" order="14">
                <![CDATA[<li>So, delivering exceptional service to customers is essential to creating loyalty… Of course, once you have captured the loyalty of a customer, you also have an added powerful benefit: Customer referrals</li>]]>
</bodyBullet>
            </ui>
