</bodyImage>
              <bodyImage id="i3" order="12" url="2220_3.jpg">
                <![CDATA[Image 3]]>
</bodyImage>
            </ui>
          </slide>
          <slide sNumber="2225" type="TextImageReplace" animType="timesync" endType="Continue">
            <ui uid="2" type="BodyText" width="680" height="180" x="center" y="270" margin="0" fontAlign="center" effect="none" time="2" trans="slideLeft" ease="QuintEaseOut" syncType="replace">
              <bodyBullet id="bb1" timeIn=".5" timeOut="999">
                <![CDATA[That’s why Chrysler Group is transitioning to CPS in many markets. Finding out the answer to that one question – and why or why not a customer would recommend you – provides valuable information that helps you build on strengths and eliminate problems. And even if you are not using CPS yet, you can still use the concept behind it to focus your improvement efforts.]]>
</bodyBullet>
            </ui>
